In Eclipse IDE we have by default Maven plugin Installed.
You Mainly need the below:
1. m2e --> maven Integration for Eclipse
2. m2e-wtp --> maven web tool project


Steps:
1. Create a new Maven project
2. Select the Arifact for the quickstart
3. click Finish

By default it will show J2SE 1.5. We need to tell maven Compiler to use maven 1.8

Add the below lines in properties tag.

<maven.compiler.target>1.8<maven.compiler.target>
<maven.compiler.source>1.8<maven.compiler.source>


=================================================================================================================

Creating a Web App using Maven

Steps:
1. Select the Artifact as webapp
2. Fill the GAV
3. Finish